  <brief_title>ASA- and Clopidogrel-Responsiveness in Patients With Peripheral Arterial Occlusive Disease and Interventional Procedures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of Laboratory Resistance to Aspirin and Clopidogrel and Its Clinical Relevance in Patients With Peripheral Arterial Occlusive Disease Requiring Interventional Procedures</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
